listing.description:
Beautifully positioned in a quiet cul de sac, Oates Breheny Group are excited to welcome this extremely well presented three bedroom semi detached home with fantastic sea views located in the sought after residential development of Dorrins Strand. 
Nestled in the heart of Strandhill this very impressive property has been tastefully decorated to provide light filled accommodation enhancing the superb views giving this home a wonderful sense of tranquility. A lovely private garden stretches out the back further enhancing its appeal. 
This beautiful property is an incredible opportunity for its new owner to reside in one of Sligo's most popular & vibrant areas.
Strandhill Village has an abundance of amenities including world class surfing beach, golf course, primary school, 
churches, pharmacy, shops, café's, pubs/restaurants, numerous walking & hiking trails and a popular Sunday  market. There is also a variety of facilities for children including sports grounds Strand Celtic Football Club & Sligo Rugby Club for extra family activities. 
Accommodation comprises of elegant living room accessible from the front with cosy insert stove and double doors to the spacious kitchen/dining area which leads out to the rear garden with stunning sea views. There is also a utility area off the kitchen and WC. Upstairs there are three bedrooms (one ensuite) all with built in wardrobes and a main family bathroom. 
Do not miss your opportunity to view this superb home by contacting our sales team on 071 9140404.
ACCOMMODATION

GROUND FLOOR

Tiled flooring

Living Room (4.71m x 4.26m)
Carpet flooring, open fireplace with marble surround and insert stove, sliding doors to front of property, double doors to kitchen/dining

Kitchen/Dining (5.42m x 3.95m)
Fully fitted kitchen with tiled flooring and between units, integrated hob, oven, extractor fan & fridge freezer unit (no fridge freezer), sliding door to rear garden

Utility Area (1.94m x 1.91m)
Tiled flooring and between units, fitted kitchen units, plumbing for washing machine and dishwasher

Tiled flooring, wc, whb

Carpet flooring, double room, built in wardrobe

Tiled floor to ceiling, wc, whb, electric shower

Carpet flooring, double room, built in wardrobe, sea views

Bedroom 3 (3.04m x 2.93m)
Carpet flooring, single room, built in wardrobe

Bathroom (2.35m x 2.71m)
Tiled floor to ceiling, wc, whb, bath
